{"tid":2046111,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"古支那文冇標點點斷句？","createTime":"2020-06-01T07:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T11:16:09.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"8b8e029124e7339b0bfa66f54505d9852f341d23","tid":2046111,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T07:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iUhSvmC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FiUhSvmC.jpg&h=9242ec72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面係明太祖聖旨<br />\n<br />\n好奇古人點斷句？又真係好難理解明太祖寫嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ebbf5335ea63eba17166398909b7649e8fdbcf","tid":2046111,"uid":302951,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:07:44.000Z","msg":"啲人就係要學係咁嘅情況下解讀文章<br />\n參考師說 : 彼童子之師，授之書而習其句讀者也。<br />\n即係話啲仔嘅老師教佢地讀書，學習斷句嘅方法"},{"pid":"1a45828673ea170972596510c1d5476202a5b17d","tid":2046111,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:15:41.000Z","msg":"習慣問題"},{"pid":"b8eb7e2beeb963a7805ae43133e067bf0fe0377a","tid":2046111,"uid":228894,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:22:33.000Z","msg":"萬一不交租 亦可收回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b101f3477fd84446247b3faee01a2e52c9e9ae","tid":2046111,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:27:25.000Z","msg":"支那文除左標點外，冇野分開句子。句子入面成分辨識好難，唔似日文咁，有は/が/です/ます/だ表示句子結束/主語位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d30784670d2ab0af9ac2db82cde92a133dec230","tid":2046111,"uid":308251,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:30:04.000Z","msg":"所以咪多冤案，屌佢老尾，我祖上本身當官，有日審單強姦案，個租客個老婆比個肥西業主屈強姦，仲話佢地交唔齊租要收返間屋，咁個租客就拎張租約出黎啦，張野就冇標點，咁個內容就大概係租客嘅祖先對肥西業主嘅祖先有恩，因此年租30蚊，寫明唔交租都得，話咁樣係報恩，點知肥西業主個律師話我祖先冇讀過書，唔識睇，應該年租30萬，唔交租就收屋，咁又真係吹佢唔脹，又冇標點，最尾咪比佢地收返間屋，我祖先就日日比人屌，左一句狗官右一句狗官，仲喺後門放陷阱，好快就鬱鬱而終。"},{"pid":"00124bae260afb3d7f586fa904d9e1f75fe7ea7a","tid":2046111,"uid":27319,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:30:45.000Z","msg":"如果有停頓位，唔係有個句號喺右下方咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3fe040859c6627ea3022e6cd716ca0f8053c048","tid":2046111,"uid":27319,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:31:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果要停頓，古人唔係習慣有個句號喺右下方咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3f58061be2cfcaf342c6cfc37db08b359cd92383","tid":2046111,"uid":65638,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T09:21:01.000Z","msg":"古人會唔會有d 蠢，發明標點都諗唔倒？"},{"pid":"4b258b8728189a02598df516067b14fcd21a6b52","tid":2046111,"uid":65638,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00124bae260afb3d7f586fa904d9e1f75fe7ea7a","tid":2046111,"uid":27319,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:30:45.000Z","msg":"如果有停頓位，唔係有個句號喺右下方咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T09:22:40.000Z","msg":"後人加，好似係"},{"pid":"4c3f473ade43749fb179b2976c62dca26086083a","tid":2046111,"uid":201031,"