(當時全部都貴價)<br />\n<br />\n再古老d,竹簡，要用刀刻上去，<br />\n<br />\n再古老d是刻在獸骨，龜甲上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n古人寫字絕無而家用原子筆咁快"},{"pid":"7b0af755031392f50fbda34f066425a4c0f00c89","tid":2046111,"uid":249885,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:37:58.000Z","msg":"講野夠無標點點解你又聽得明人地講野"},{"pid":"a4a6050dfc8a6e3a494a6f4fa14f10cef1a6f2d8","tid":2046111,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:41:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/19646540\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F19646540&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns80PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=21712f83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/19646540</a>"},{"pid":"7e9c3678255999b574520a99351b265f00ba54c1","tid":2046111,"uid":107540,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b0af755031392f50fbda34f066425a4c0f00c89","tid":2046111,"uid":249885,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:37:58.000Z","msg":"講野夠無標點點解你又聽得明人地講野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:43:45.000Z","msg":"呢個比喻有啲牽強<br />\n說話本身有停頓位置<br />\n比如你句子與句子之間係有停一停嘅時間<br />\n嗰啲已經係個標點符號<br />\n只不過睇唔到係聽出嚟<br />\n上面書寫個例子係完全連住<br />\n除非佢有空格咁隔開<br />\n如果唔係你個比喻唔成立喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764b27e1d6652a4f5a13f1a5c1e64654d962a0c7","tid":2046111,"uid":317956,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:50:39.000Z","msg":"文言文有古定句法，其實同日文一樣"},{"pid":"9b7a0c4d1f6e81251414893c8eeeab2114e98cdc","tid":2046111,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7e9c3678255999b574520a99351b265f00ba54c1","tid":2046111,"uid":107540,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b0af755031392f50fbda34f066425a4c0f00c89","tid":2046111,"uid":249885,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:37:58.000Z","msg":"講野夠無標點點解你又聽得明人地講野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:43:45.000Z","msg":"呢個比喻有啲牽強<br />\n說話本